<concept id="concept_E8D43EB4494E41D2AB42D4A89396D1AB"
                    xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Removing Metrics Data</title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p>Metrics data is stored in the Metrics and Alarms Database, an InfluxDB database.</p>
            <note othertype="note">
                <p>The InfluxDB version that is integrated into the current version of <ph
                        conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                    /> does not feature reliable mechanisms for deleting outdated or unnecessary metrics data from a clustered database.</p>
            </note>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
